message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product which I believe would significantly enhance your operations or personal needs. Given its exceptional value and quality, it's worth noting that the product is valued at $12000 by you. Considering this, I am offering you the opportunity to acquire it at an exclusive price of $10000. This offer is tailored to ensure you receive a substantial benefit while also maximizing the return on my investment. I look forward to your consideration.
